The paper combines methods from Deep Learning and Program Synthesis fields, which are typically associated with sub-categories such as cs.AI, cs.PL, and cs.LG. The focus on designing a domain-specific language (DSL) and defining an efficient search algorithm suggests a connection to cs.SE. Finally, the use of natural language processing techniques to generate programs from descriptions and examples suggests a connection to cs.CL.
